<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.5.8">
<l>pārmaṉṉar maṅkap paṭaitoṭṭu veñcamattu</l>
<l>tērmaṉṉark kāyaṉṟu tērūrntāṉ kāṇēṭī</l>
<l>tērmaṉṉark kāyaṉṟu tērūrntā ṉākilum</l>
<l>tārmaṉṉar taṅkaḷ talaimēlāṉ cāḻalē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>See, Friend! Taking up weapons so that the kings of the earth were ruined,</l>
<l>He drove a chariot that day in heated battle for the chariot warrior.</l>
<l>Although he drove a chariot that day for the chariot warrior,</l>
<l>He is the one on the heads of the garlanded kings. Cāḻalē!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
